識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n植物係唔係生命 有冇意識"},{"pid":"600421eac8a486b903485a7554ee3759c54c3aaf","tid":388624,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算吧啦<br />\n<br />\n有D素食者係都要兜，話咩野植物冇意識，唔會sense到痛苦...甚麼甚麼<br />\n<br />\n個事實係，你唔係動物，就得返植物食，否則你會死<br />\n<br />\n你係人，你怕死，你想生存，所以你要食植物生存落去<br />\n<br />\n利申 素食</blockquote><br />\n咁呢啲又唔係進食嘅理由，係選擇素食嘅理由呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n人要生存係一定要食嘢，可以咩都食，又可以食素，咁點解選擇素食，背後總有理由㗎，有人因為健康，有人因為宗教，有人因為道德信念，「植物無意識」呢啲嘢正正係某派道德理由嘅基礎嚟<br />\n<br />\n除非你認為佢地表面理由與真實理由唔同啫，如果唔係點解話「植物無意識」之類係兜？"},{"pid":"9cb10b9bca10cb58b05a9842ce13b9b853c86060","tid":388624,"uid":3180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"其實唔可以純粹因爲唔鍾意食肉所以食素咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋食得多肉個人好易病（唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n咩都要因為宗教/覺得殘忍而批評啲素食者有咩為？<br />\n<br />\n利申：鍾意食素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得好味過肉"},{"pid":"998157b757126c3db987e5e44d3c15d839e52b86","tid":388624,"uid":101508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:34:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有生命同有意識係兩件事嚟</blockquote><br />\n有生命既野會無意識架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聾啞殘廢既人一定無意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nup乜鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw on9 素食者"},{"pid":"955d46c5ee4e977a6ef56ae4b4365f2d8efd3608","tid":388624,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc